    <title>石头剪刀布</title>
    <link href="http://hexoproject.github.io/2025/05/15/%E7%9F%B3%E5%A4%B4%E5%89%AA%E5%88%80%E5%B8%83/"/>
    <id>http://hexoproject.github.io/2025/05/15/%E7%9F%B3%E5%A4%B4%E5%89%AA%E5%88%80%E5%B8%83/</id>
    <published>2025-05-15T07:34:48.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-05-17T03:39:32.598Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;stdint.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;time.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line">#include &lt;stdlib.h&gt;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">#define u32 uint32_t</span><br><span class="line">#define ROCK 1</span><br><span class="line">#define PAPER 2</span><br><span class="line">#define SCISSORS 3</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">void destemine_winner(u32 player_move, u32 computer_move)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">//首先排除平局的情况</span><br><span class="line">if (player_move == computer_move) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;平局！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//定义一个胜利的规则映射，其中键是玩家的移动，值是玩家移动可以打败计算机的移动</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">u32 winning_moves[4] = &#123; 0, SCISSORS, ROCK, PAPER &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">//0是占位符</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//winning_moves[1] SCISSORS</span><br><span class="line">//ROCK == 1</span><br><span class="line">//PAPER == 2</span><br><span class="line">//SCISSORS == 3</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//这里player_move是玩家的移动，winning_moves[player_move]这个是可以打败计算机的移动</span><br><span class="line">//比如说玩家选1，只有当计算机选3时才会输，那么就将winning_moves中的winning_moves[1]设置位3</span><br><span class="line">if (computer_move == winning_moves[player_move]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;你赢了！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;你输了！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">u32 get_player_choice() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">u32 choice;</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;请选择：1是石头，2是布，3是剪刀&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">scanf_s(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;choice);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">while (choice &lt; ROCK || choice &gt; SCISSORS) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;无效选择！请重新选择：1是石头，2是布，3是剪刀&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">scanf_s(&quot;%d&quot;, &amp;choice);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">return choice;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">u32 get_computer_choice() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">return (rand() % (SCISSORS - ROCK + 1)) + ROCK;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">void print_instructions() &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;石头~剪刀~布，游戏开始！&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;规则：输入数字，确定猜拳。1是石头，2是布，3是剪刀&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;==========================================&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">void print_choice(u32 choice) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">switch (choice)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">case ROCK: puts(&quot;石头&quot;); break;</span><br><span class="line">case PAPER: puts(&quot;布&quot;); break;</span><br><span class="line">case SCISSORS: puts(&quot;剪刀&quot;); break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">int main(void)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">//初始化随机数生成器</span><br><span class="line">srand(time(NULL));</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//打印游戏说明</span><br><span class="line">print_instructions();</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//获取玩家和计算机的选择</span><br><span class="line">u32 player_choice = get_player_choice();</span><br><span class="line">u32 computer_choice = get_computer_choice();</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//展示玩家和计算器的选择</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;你选择了&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">print_choice(player_choice);</span><br><span class="line">puts(&quot;计算机选择了&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">print_choice(computer_choice);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">//判断确认赢家，并且展示</span><br><span class="line">destemine_winner(player_choice, computer_choice);</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
